title: Crescent City 1127 Highway 101 N. Thurs-Sun. 10am-3pm
text: Thurs-Sun. 10am-3pm Living Estate Sale. Flea Market grounds. Accumulation from pole barn, garages, with more stuff added daily. Mostly guy stuff, tons of Harley stuff. Evos/shovels, hand & electric tools, welders, calipers, Toyota motorhome, Honda Elite scooters, auto tires, go-cart frame, parts, tires & motors, $2 DVDs, jeans, bike parts, 8x12 shed. 707-218-5815
